// CHALLENGE: uncomment the code below and see the car stats rendered import React from "react"; import ReactDOM from "react-dom"; import cars from "./practice" const [honda, tesla] = cars //Tesla Components const {coloursByPopularity: [teslaTopColour] , speedStats: {topSpeed : teslaTopSpeed }} = tesla //Honda Components const {coloursByPopularity: [hondaTopColuor], speedStats: {topSpeed : hondaTopSpeed}} = honda ReactDOM.render(
Brand Top Speed Top Color
{tesla.model} {teslaTopSpeed} {teslaTopColour}
{honda.model} {hondaTopSpeed} {hondaTopColour}
, document.getElementById("root") );
